<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy - RankTiers</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body class="bg-neutral-900 text-white font-sans">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
      Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %>
    </p>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We collect information you provide when registering for an account, such as your email address and Minecraft username. 
        If you use our Discord bot, we may also collect your Discord user ID and messages related to testing requests.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <p>
        Data is used to manage your player profile, track tiers, kits, and points, 
        and to provide testing queue features through Discord. 
        We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
      <p>
        All information is stored securely via Supabase. 
        We take reasonable precautions to protect your data from unauthorized access.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Our site may use cookies to keep you logged in and improve your experience.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at 
        <a href="mailto:support@ranktiers.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">support@ranktiers.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <a href="/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
